{"tid":1306710,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"入一入黎傾 （今次遊行集中返黑警暴力濫權到）！！！推","createTime":"2019-07-11T09:03:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T09:58:09.000Z","uid":209678,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"680efc7950d1a0efa215d865dd8312ea08cf1ff3","tid":1306710,"uid":209678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T09:03:11.000Z","msg":"連儂牆要整係ok唔反對，不過唔好掛住整而忽略左遊行示威，寄意既野有心邊到都係連儂牆，<span style=\"color: red;\">切勿上心</span><br />\n<br />\n本人係覺得大家點逼林奠都係唔會講 撤回 所以我地今次目標要係全體警務人員 事實我地終極目標係撤回惡法，但今次<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">當</span>佢延後左先，我地更加要盡快打擊黑警。<br />\n<br />\n只要剷除到到黑警，警察內部佢哋就唔會上心落力做政苦隻狗，其實對我地目標更進一步，少左阻礙。<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好俾之前所有犧牲浪費。其實五大訴求係可以 隨意調前後架，唔好咁死板，一定要非第一樣先，最近邊樣埋身啲，咪做個樣先囉<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5341ffe505241cf6c821b56baddd79d5e7b39712","tid":1306710,"uid":209678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T09:03:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b9daf18274ac7967f94b0cb5bea12cc53c400d58","tid":1306710,"uid":209678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T09:04:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f3cc8c0ac23b9a1172c99c24eb973c8a9c3beb45","tid":1306710,"uid":258696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T09:04:35.000Z","msg":"【任務欄】<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1306215\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1306215</a><br />\n任務眾多，請自行因應人數及背後目的考慮做邊D任 ；黃色為主線任務；紅色係Boss <br />\n7.11 - 梁烈士公眾告別禮 - <a href=\"http://t.me/leung711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fleung711&d=i5E3ds%2FeSPFE00WLmt8525gFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=c33870d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/leung711</a><br />\n7.11 - 油尖旺區議會夢遊 - <a href=\"http://t.me/ytm_dc711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fytm_dc711&d=i5E3ds%2FeSPFE00WLmt8525gFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=0300cbd8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ht